   By [39]KEVIN ROBILLARD | 5/1/13 9:57 AM EDT Updated: 5/1/13 4:31 PM EDT

   Controversial freshman Sen. Ted Cruz is considering a 2016 presidential
   run, according to a report.

   "Ted won't be opening an Iowa office anytime soon, but he's listening,"
   an anonymous longtime friend of Cruz's told [40]National Review. "This
   is all in the early stages; nothing is official. It's just building on
   its own."
